Unwind with Rewined Candle and Zibibbo
List.Description:
Unwind by lighting a Rewined candle and opening a bottle of Zibibbo Sparkling Pink Moscato. These luxury candles are made from repurposed wine bottles, and filled with oils carefully blended to develop a fragrance that embraces the delicious flavors and aromas of Champagne. Coupled with this long lasting candle is a bottle of Angove Family Winemakers Zibibbo, a South Australian wine that has a delightfully sweet taste and delicate flavor. Light effervescence and vibrant strawberry notes are complemented by red berry fruit overtones and a fresh finish. This makes a great gift for wine lovers, candle lovers, or those who love all things green.

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Angove Family Winemakers Zibibbo Sparkling Pink Moscato:
    Incredibly floral and heady muscat (aka zibbibo); will undoubtedly gain some yardage from the name (and aroma). Enjoy in a champagne flute while noshing on strawberries or enjoy a glass as a perfect finish to your long day.

  • Rewined Signature Wine Bottle Candle
    11 oz hand poured premium soy wax candle. This glass container is hand crafted from recycled wine bottles. The luxurious candle fragrance is inspired by the Champagne wine varietal.

    Due to the popularity of this gift, vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage.

Bella Cucina Antipasti Gift Set
List.Description:
Crisp Prosecco straight from Italy and delicious foods from Bella Cucina - this beautiful gift set is sure to be thoroughly enjoyed!

Gift Set Includes:

  • Ruffino Prosecco:
    Ruffino Prosecco has been produced from grapes grown in the hilly area of Valdobbiadene, which is the most historically vocated region for the production of Prosecco. Bright straw yellow with fine bubbles. The bouquet is fragrant and intensely fruity. It shows clean notes of apples, pears and citrus, accompanied by slight hints of hawthorn, wisteria and elder. Crisp, clean and delicate with fine bubble caressing. Intense sensations of apples and peaches drive a pleasant aftertaste, that is reminiscent of fruity and floral aromas.

  • Bella Cucina Artichoke Pesto Dip :
    Bella Cucina’s most popular pesto, this dip combines artichoke hearts at their peak and the richness of olive oil and Parmesan cheese. 6 oz.

  • Bella Cucina Olivada Olive Pesto Dip:
    Olive pesto dip handmade with pure kalamata olives and a hint of lemon. 6 oz..

  • Bella Cucina Preserved Lemon Cream:
    Finely diced preserved lemons folded into a tangy lemon cream. 6 oz.
  • Bella Cucina Dipping Crackers:
    Savory cracker rounds perfect for dipping into appetizer spreads. 10 oz.

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York and Connecticut, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.
